metric formulation of tensor hierarchies and gauged supergravity. In\nparticular, we will provide a global formulation of generalised Scherk-Schwarz\nreductions and we will discuss their global non-geometric properties. Finally,\nwe explore the T-duality covariant geometric quantisation of DFT.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Aug 2021 17:14:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-24"}
