isalignment. With a single alignment, our method achieves 8.81 arcmin (1.37\nmm) positional error and 1.76 degree rotational error by camera-based tests in\nthe arm-reach distance, and 10.79 arcmin (7.71 pixels) reprojection error by\nuser tests.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 Aug 2021 09:34:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-25"}
